post.content:
Hi Everyone,

We have another Munching for Music date!

When: Thursday, October 29 from 5pm to 8pm

Where: Five Guys at South Park Mall in Strongsville

What: Show this flier or simply mention that you are there to support the band when you order, and up to 25% of your purchase will be donated to us.

Enjoy some great food and help the band at the same time!
